1
00:00:06,170 --> 00:00:07,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No, she got overtaken!</font>

2
00:00:07,790 --> 00:00:10,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Those guys are way too fast.</font>

3
00:00:10,080 --> 00:00:11,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Aw, she finished last.</font>

4
00:00:11,960 --> 00:00:14,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Luck of the draw, I guess.</font>

5
00:00:14,290 --> 00:00:16,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We have to bid farewell
to everyone who lost.</font>

6
00:00:16,630 --> 00:00:20,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Winners, please move
to the waiting room.</font>

7
00:00:20,540 --> 00:00:24,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's still amazing that she got an invite
from such a big-name VTuber.</font>

8
00:00:24,420 --> 00:00:26,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yamabuki-kun helped her out, apparently.</font>

9
00:00:26,790 --> 00:00:29,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He sure loves to poke his nose
into everything.</font>

10
00:00:29,380 --> 00:00:33,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He sent me like ten pamphlets
for voice acting schools, too.</font>

11
00:00:33,580 --> 00:00:36,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He also scheduled
my street performance without asking.</font>

12
00:00:36,790 --> 00:00:39,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">With that kind of zeal,
he could be a stalker.</font>

13
00:00:39,710 --> 00:00:40,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't say that.</font>

14
00:00:40,960 --> 00:00:42,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Aww.</font>

15
00:02:19,960 --> 00:02:22,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}FURIN HIGH SCHOOL</font>

16
00:02:24,040 --> 00:02:27,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The lunch broadcast will have
a new segment starting this week.</font>

17
00:02:27,500 --> 00:02:28,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I can't wait!</font>

18
00:02:28,960 --> 00:02:30,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I should clean my ears.</font>

19
00:02:30,790 --> 00:02:31,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Gross!</font>

20
00:02:34,130 --> 00:02:35,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Good luck, Shinobu!</font>

21
00:02:36,080 --> 00:02:37,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thanks.</font>

22
00:02:37,420 --> 00:02:39,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm looking forward to the new segment.</font>

23
00:02:39,960 --> 00:02:41,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll make sure it's fun.</font>

24
00:02:42,540 --> 00:02:44,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Won't you eat, Nene-chan?</font>

25
00:02:44,000 --> 00:02:45,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm dieting.</font>

26
00:02:47,750 --> 00:02:49,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You can do it, Nene-chan!</font>

27
00:02:49,580 --> 00:02:51,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Break a leg!</font>

28
00:02:55,630 --> 00:02:57,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Inohana-senpai.</font>

29
00:02:58,040 --> 00:02:59,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Have some cookies.</font>

30
00:02:59,500 --> 00:03:01,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Snack on them during the broadcast.</font>

31
00:03:02,880 --> 00:03:03,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thanks.</font>

32
00:03:07,710 --> 00:03:10,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Iko-chan, the broadcast is about to start.</font>

33
00:03:19,580 --> 00:03:21,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wonder what's for lunch today.</font>

34
00:03:21,880 --> 00:03:24,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Dad went all-out, so I'm excited!</font>

35
00:03:28,960 --> 00:03:31,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yikes, my stomach might rumble.</font>

36
00:03:31,500 --> 00:03:34,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Maybe I'll just eat a rice ball.</font>

37
00:03:34,580 --> 00:03:37,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You were smiling in your sleep.
Did you have a nice dream?</font>

38
00:03:38,380 --> 00:03:39,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Not telling you.</font>

39
00:03:39,960 --> 00:03:42,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}BROADCASTING ROOM (TEMP)</font>

40
00:03:43,580 --> 00:03:47,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This is the broadcasting club
with your lunch broadcast.</font>

41
00:03:47,460 --> 00:03:51,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Exciting news! We're using
brand-new equipment today!</font>

42
00:03:53,500 --> 00:03:55,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Did any of you notice?</font>

43
00:03:55,500 --> 00:03:57,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There should be much less static now.</font>

44
00:03:57,630 --> 00:04:01,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We'll keep updating our content, too.
Look forward to it.</font>

45
00:04:01,250 --> 00:04:06,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let's kick off our new segment:
Four Friends Give Love Advice!</font>

46
00:04:07,130 --> 00:04:10,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Our first message is from someone
with the pen name "Nekko-san."</font>

47
00:04:10,380 --> 00:04:12,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah, this is easier on the ears.</font>

48
00:04:12,500 --> 00:04:14,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So soothing.</font>

49
00:04:15,790 --> 00:04:20,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">"I think my boyfriend's been cheating,
but I'm too scared to confront him."</font>

50
00:04:20,170 --> 00:04:22,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What a bummer of a topic to start with.</font>

51
00:04:22,130 --> 00:04:23,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Just dump him.</font>

52
00:04:23,710 --> 00:04:26,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hack into his phone and look through it.</font>

53
00:04:26,460 --> 00:04:28,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Cheat on him as payback.</font>

54
00:04:28,080 --> 00:04:30,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How spiteful can you be?!</font>

55
00:04:31,130 --> 00:04:33,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hmm, well...</font>

56
00:04:34,460 --> 00:04:38,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Peek at his phone, and if he is cheating,
get a new boyfriend and dump him!</font>

57
00:04:38,750 --> 00:04:40,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're the most spiteful one here!</font>

58
00:04:40,920 --> 00:04:43,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's what makes Shinobu-chan great.</font>

59
00:04:43,830 --> 00:04:46,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Aren't you going to join them, Yamabuki?</font>

60
00:04:46,790 --> 00:04:49,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I don't happen to be
an expert on romance.</font>

61
00:04:49,330 --> 00:04:52,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Even if I were there,
I'd just be their hype man.</font>

62
00:04:52,420 --> 00:04:56,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Talk about first-world problems!
I'd kill to be Shinobu-chan's hype man!</font>

63
00:04:56,920 --> 00:04:59,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Besides, I can't walk them
through everything.</font>

64
00:04:59,670 --> 00:05:02,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Those four need to be able to
do this on their own.</font>

65
00:05:03,500 --> 00:05:04,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thank you for this meal.</font>

66
00:05:05,170 --> 00:05:06,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let me go buy some dessert.</font>

67
00:05:06,750 --> 00:05:08,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Big eater, much?</font>

68
00:05:08,750 --> 00:05:09,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Now...</font>

69
00:05:09,750 --> 00:05:11,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">On to our next message.</font>

70
00:05:11,380 --> 00:05:13,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's from "Itachi-san."</font>

71
00:05:13,380 --> 00:05:15,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">"There's someone I'm interested in.</font>

72
00:05:15,960 --> 00:05:18,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Whenever we make eye contact,
they bashfully turn away.</font>

73
00:05:18,460 --> 00:05:20,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Does this mean I've got a shot?"</font>

74
00:05:20,210 --> 00:05:23,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wow, how bittersweet! Puppy love!</font>

75
00:05:23,000 --> 00:05:24,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Th-That's naughty!</font>

76
00:05:24,750 --> 00:05:26,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What do you think, Shinobu?</font>

77
00:05:27,920 --> 00:05:30,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Turn away, huh?</font>

78
00:05:30,250 --> 00:05:31,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well...</font>

79
00:05:49,380 --> 00:05:51,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You've got a shot, all right.</font>

80
00:05:51,420 --> 00:05:54,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why are you blushing, Shinobu?</font>

81
00:05:54,040 --> 00:05:56,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I think you're jumping to conclusions.</font>

82
00:05:56,880 --> 00:05:57,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Itachi-chan.</font>

83
00:05:57,830 --> 00:06:00,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Keep us posted, okay?</font>

84
00:06:03,080 --> 00:06:05,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}BROADCASTING ROOM (TEMP)
THE NEXT DAY</font>

85
00:06:05,500 --> 00:06:08,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thank you for all your
messages today as well.</font>

86
00:06:08,960 --> 00:06:10,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let's start with "Itachi-san."</font>

87
00:06:10,460 --> 00:06:15,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">"We made plans to go out for dinner.
What should we get?"</font>

88
00:06:15,500 --> 00:06:18,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wow, making good progress!</font>

89
00:06:18,080 --> 00:06:19,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You were right about having a shot.</font>

90
00:06:19,630 --> 00:06:22,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They're going out for dinner already?
That's kinda naughty.</font>

91
00:06:22,920 --> 00:06:24,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Doesn't the love interest
seem sleazy?</font>

92
00:06:24,830 --> 00:06:27,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What would be a good choice for dinner?</font>

93
00:06:27,170 --> 00:06:28,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You need to show you have good taste.</font>

94
00:06:28,920 --> 00:06:30,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's your pick, Iko?</font>

95
00:06:30,960 --> 00:06:33,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If it were me, hmm...</font>

96
00:06:37,040 --> 00:06:40,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This is my first time eating
okonomiyaki at a restaurant.</font>

97
00:06:40,250 --> 00:06:42,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The thermal energy
of the griddle's scaring me.</font>

98
00:06:42,880 --> 00:06:45,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You just need to flip it over
and sauce it up.</font>

99
00:06:45,880 --> 00:06:47,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Okay, I'll flip it over.</font>

100
00:06:47,880 --> 00:06:49,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Be careful.</font>

101
00:06:51,670 --> 00:06:53,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This is hard.</font>

102
00:06:54,330 --> 00:06:56,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're so silly, Iko.</font>

103
00:07:01,130 --> 00:07:04,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Listen, you can't be too rough with it.</font>

104
00:07:04,830 --> 00:07:08,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Gently caress it like this.</font>

105
00:07:09,000 --> 00:07:11,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Okonomiyaki, I guess?</font>

106
00:07:11,630 --> 00:07:13,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's a surprise.</font>

107
00:07:13,330 --> 00:07:16,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Good idea, though.
It has entertainment value, too.</font>

108
00:07:16,670 --> 00:07:20,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Iko-chan likes okonomiyaki, huh?</font>

109
00:07:20,040 --> 00:07:22,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'd love to go get some with her.</font>

110
00:07:26,170 --> 00:07:29,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We've received another
message from Itachi-san.</font>

111
00:07:29,790 --> 00:07:32,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">"We've got the perfect mood
going right now.</font>

112
00:07:33,080 --> 00:07:35,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm so close!
What should I do to seal the deal?</font>

113
00:07:35,960 --> 00:07:38,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm so nervous! I can't speak!"</font>

114
00:07:38,130 --> 00:07:39,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Right now?!</font>

115
00:07:39,170 --> 00:07:40,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's so hype!</font>

116
00:07:40,670 --> 00:07:43,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They're doing something naughty
somewhere in this school!</font>

117
00:07:43,830 --> 00:07:45,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How to seal the deal, huh?</font>

118
00:07:45,580 --> 00:07:48,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sounds like asking them out
will do the trick!</font>

119
00:07:48,670 --> 00:07:50,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Too nervous to speak, remember?</font>

120
00:07:50,880 --> 00:07:53,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You've got it in the bag.</font>

121
00:07:53,330 --> 00:07:55,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I bet my fried chicken on this going well.</font>

122
00:07:55,790 --> 00:07:58,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The next move is a no-brainer, then.</font>

123
00:07:58,250 --> 00:07:59,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Easy-peasy.</font>

124
00:08:00,210 --> 00:08:00,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Just...</font>

125
00:08:00,960 --> 00:08:03,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">- Just go for a hug.
- Just go for a kiss.</font>

126
00:08:03,710 --> 00:08:04,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">- Huh?
- Huh?</font>

127
00:08:06,080 --> 00:08:08,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You can't just kiss someone, Nene.</font>

128
00:08:08,540 --> 00:08:10,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Have you lost all sense of social norms?</font>

129
00:08:10,500 --> 00:08:13,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wha? Just so you know,
I'm talking about a kiss on the cheek.</font>

130
00:08:13,920 --> 00:08:15,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And you, jumping right to a hug?</font>

131
00:08:15,960 --> 00:08:18,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Do you randomly cling to people
like a bitch in heat?</font>

132
00:08:19,170 --> 00:08:21,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hugging is how people greet
each other in the West.</font>

133
00:08:21,790 --> 00:08:24,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Same for cheek kisses.</font>

134
00:08:24,670 --> 00:08:28,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Shinobu, let's turn the mic off.
I sense a catfight incoming.</font>

135
00:08:28,170 --> 00:08:29,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Agreed!</font>

136
00:08:29,960 --> 00:08:32,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Calm down, you two.</font>

137
00:08:32,330 --> 00:08:35,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This is getting a bit out of hand,
don't you think?</font>

138
00:08:35,580 --> 00:08:38,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We can't give advice on stuff
we have no experience with.</font>

139
00:08:38,920 --> 00:08:40,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">- I do have experience, though?
- I do have experience, though?</font>

140
00:08:41,290 --> 00:08:42,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?</font>

141
00:08:42,710 --> 00:08:45,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, um, sorry about that.</font>

142
00:08:45,250 --> 00:08:46,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Way to fold, Shinobu!</font>

143
00:08:46,710 --> 00:08:48,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">My hug was effective.</font>

144
00:08:48,290 --> 00:08:50,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So was my kiss!</font>

145
00:08:54,330 --> 00:08:56,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey, you like hugs more, don't you?</font>

146
00:08:56,960 --> 00:08:58,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You prefer a kiss, right?</font>

147
00:08:58,880 --> 00:09:00,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Which...</font>

148
00:09:00,170 --> 00:09:01,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">...do you prefer?</font>

149
00:09:01,830 --> 00:09:03,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Tell us!</font>

150
00:09:08,000 --> 00:09:09,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Say, Yamabuki-kun.</font>

151
00:09:09,960 --> 00:09:12,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What makes you happier? A kiss or a hug?</font>

152
00:09:12,420 --> 00:09:14,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>She's still not backing down?!</i></font>

153
00:09:15,170 --> 00:09:17,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No need to be shy.</font>

154
00:09:17,500 --> 00:09:20,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We've turned the mic off.</font>

155
00:09:20,080 --> 00:09:21,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Uh...</font>

156
00:09:21,130 --> 00:09:23,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The mic is still on, actually.</font>

157
00:09:23,580 --> 00:09:27,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I knew Inohana-san and Himekawa-san
would have the experience.</font>

158
00:09:27,250 --> 00:09:29,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I want Rikka-chan to hug me!</font>

159
00:09:29,420 --> 00:09:31,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I want a kiss from Nene-chan!</font>

160
00:09:31,210 --> 00:09:33,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sorry, I hit the wrong switch.</font>

161
00:09:33,750 --> 00:09:35,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Shinobu, you big dummy!</font>

162
00:09:35,790 --> 00:09:38,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yikes, way to tank my image!</font>

163
00:09:39,630 --> 00:09:42,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let's end the broadcast.</font>

164
00:09:42,460 --> 00:09:45,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But what about our advice
for Itachi-chan?</font>

165
00:09:45,750 --> 00:09:48,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Probably doesn't need it.</font>

166
00:09:48,540 --> 00:09:51,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ugh, what a disaster.</font>

167
00:09:51,580 --> 00:09:54,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh? What a pleasant surprise, Lemon-chan.</font>

168
00:09:54,170 --> 00:09:58,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Would you let your beautiful
teacher vent for a minute?</font>

169
00:09:58,750 --> 00:10:01,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't fix your makeup in our clubroom.</font>

170
00:10:01,580 --> 00:10:03,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You know Samejima-sensei?</font>

171
00:10:03,790 --> 00:10:06,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What, that muscles-with-limbs monster?</font>

172
00:10:06,710 --> 00:10:09,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We've been making more eye contact lately.</font>

173
00:10:09,710 --> 00:10:11,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I kept turning away,</font>

174
00:10:11,790 --> 00:10:14,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but he suddenly invited me out
for okonomiyaki yesterday.</font>

175
00:10:15,000 --> 00:10:19,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I went, because free food, but he got
this idea he had a real shot with me.</font>

176
00:10:20,500 --> 00:10:22,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">When we were alone
a few moments ago...</font>

177
00:10:25,630 --> 00:10:29,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">he tried to kiss and hug me all
at once, so I kicked his ass.</font>

178
00:10:29,500 --> 00:10:32,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Dude, you were Itachi-chan?!</i></font>

179
00:10:35,460 --> 00:10:38,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">By the way, your broadcast
was really something.</font>

180
00:10:38,330 --> 00:10:41,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I never knew you girls
were so experienced.</font>

181
00:10:41,420 --> 00:10:44,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't get the wrong idea!
That was all lies!</font>

182
00:10:44,290 --> 00:10:46,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Inohana isn't denying it, though?</font>

183
00:10:46,750 --> 00:10:49,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why aren't you saying anything, Rikka?!</font>

184
00:10:49,210 --> 00:10:50,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Maybe they do need me around.</i></font>

185
00:10:50,960 --> 00:10:53,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}KISS OR HUG</font>

186
00:10:53,960 --> 00:10:56,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}FURIN HIGH SCHOOL</font>

187
00:10:56,880 --> 00:11:00,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Today's broadcasts
were all a work of fiction.</font>

188
00:11:00,750 --> 00:11:06,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Any resemblance to actual persons,
groups, or events is purely coincidental.</font>

189
00:11:06,790 --> 00:11:10,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, we hope you have a good afternoon!</font>

190
00:11:11,540 --> 00:11:12,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There.</font>

191
00:11:13,920 --> 00:11:18,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, I don't really care
if you tank your image or not,</font>

192
00:11:18,750 --> 00:11:21,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but keep the romance
talk on the down-low.</font>

193
00:11:24,500 --> 00:11:25,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yikes.</font>

194
00:11:25,250 --> 00:11:26,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's raining.</font>

195
00:11:26,750 --> 00:11:27,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, wow.</font>

196
00:11:27,710 --> 00:11:30,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Right, I forgot.
Do you have a minute, Iko?</font>

197
00:11:31,790 --> 00:11:34,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let's plan out your next stream.</font>

198
00:11:34,040 --> 00:11:35,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Okie-dokie.</font>

199
00:11:35,290 --> 00:11:40,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is it just me, or is the errand boy
calling her "Iko" lately?</font>

200
00:11:40,170 --> 00:11:41,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Nope, it's not just you.</font>

201
00:11:41,420 --> 00:11:44,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Those two have been pretty close lately.</font>

202
00:11:44,380 --> 00:11:45,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Quite literally, yes.</font>

203
00:11:45,880 --> 00:11:46,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Next time—</font>

204
00:11:46,750 --> 00:11:48,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey, errand boy?</font>

205
00:11:48,460 --> 00:11:49,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">My name is Yamabuki.</font>

206
00:11:49,880 --> 00:11:53,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How come you're calling
Iko by her first name?</font>

207
00:11:53,040 --> 00:11:56,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, sorry. I didn't really notice.</font>

208
00:11:56,000 --> 00:11:59,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We've spent much time together lately,
so I'm more casual around her.</font>

209
00:11:59,580 --> 00:12:01,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Time together?</font>

210
00:12:01,170 --> 00:12:02,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Forgive me, Kirino.</font>

211
00:12:02,420 --> 00:12:04,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It was rude of me to use your first name.</font>

212
00:12:04,540 --> 00:12:05,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Not really.</font>

213
00:12:05,960 --> 00:12:08,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I don't mind.</font>

214
00:12:09,290 --> 00:12:10,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is that so?</font>

215
00:12:10,960 --> 00:12:13,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll keep calling you Iko, then.
It's easier.</font>

216
00:12:13,210 --> 00:12:14,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll allow it.</font>

217
00:12:14,290 --> 00:12:16,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah, yeah, okay, okay.</font>

218
00:12:16,710 --> 00:12:20,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Fine, I'll make
a special exception for you.</font>

219
00:12:20,130 --> 00:12:21,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What is it?</font>

220
00:12:21,670 --> 00:12:26,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll let you call me N-Nene, too.</font>

221
00:12:26,420 --> 00:12:27,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why?</font>

222
00:12:27,330 --> 00:12:30,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Because it's easier to say, too!</font>

223
00:12:30,330 --> 00:12:33,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Himekawa is four syllables,
while Nene is only two!</font>

224
00:12:33,830 --> 00:12:35,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You'll save so much time!</font>

225
00:12:35,540 --> 00:12:37,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">O-Okay.</font>

226
00:12:38,250 --> 00:12:39,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Nene.</font>

227
00:12:45,130 --> 00:12:48,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey, Inohana. What's gotten into her?</font>

228
00:12:48,210 --> 00:12:49,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Rikka.</font>

229
00:12:50,420 --> 00:12:52,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You can call me Rikka, too.</font>

230
00:12:53,580 --> 00:12:55,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If you say so.</font>

231
00:12:55,170 --> 00:12:56,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Try it out.</font>

232
00:12:57,630 --> 00:12:58,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Rikka.</font>

233
00:13:00,250 --> 00:13:01,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That tickles the ear.</font>

234
00:13:01,920 --> 00:13:03,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What is going on here?!</font>

235
00:13:03,250 --> 00:13:04,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't get flustered, boy.</font>

236
00:13:04,580 --> 00:13:05,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I am not!</font>

237
00:13:07,210 --> 00:13:10,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The way this is going, should I call you
by your first name too, Uzuki?</font>

238
00:13:12,290 --> 00:13:15,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I think I'll pass.
It's too embarrassing for me.</font>

239
00:13:15,960 --> 00:13:17,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">All right.</font>

240
00:13:17,130 --> 00:13:19,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Aww, look who just got rejected.</font>

241
00:13:19,330 --> 00:13:20,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Stop that, Nene.</font>

242
00:13:22,830 --> 00:13:24,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Your face is all red. Do you have a cold?</font>

243
00:13:25,500 --> 00:13:27,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Should we cancel today's study session?</font>

244
00:13:27,790 --> 00:13:29,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Nah, I'm fine.</font>

245
00:13:29,790 --> 00:13:32,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Okay, I'll see you at the usual diner.</font>

246
00:13:35,500 --> 00:13:39,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Shinobu's been getting you to tutor her?</font>

247
00:13:39,540 --> 00:13:44,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It was Bucky's idea,
since anchors need smarts.</font>

248
00:13:44,580 --> 00:13:47,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Being tutored by the
errand boy must be a pain.</font>

249
00:13:56,130 --> 00:13:58,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The answer for that is #2.</font>

250
00:13:58,330 --> 00:13:59,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Look at the preposition again.</font>

251
00:13:59,880 --> 00:14:03,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, I see. That was careless of me.</font>

252
00:14:03,710 --> 00:14:07,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">For long questions, first try
to find where the subject is.</font>

253
00:14:08,290 --> 00:14:12,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ignore the terms you don't know
and read the whole passage first.</font>

254
00:14:14,130 --> 00:14:16,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That sounds really crispy.</font>

255
00:14:17,170 --> 00:14:20,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I got lucky with really fresh fries.
Want half?</font>

256
00:14:20,830 --> 00:14:23,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm dieting, so I'll just have one.</font>

257
00:14:23,920 --> 00:14:25,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hold it.</font>

258
00:14:25,170 --> 00:14:28,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If you go in with your hand, you'll get
oil all over your pen and notebook.</font>

259
00:14:29,250 --> 00:14:30,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Here.</font>

260
00:14:31,250 --> 00:14:33,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Whoa, seriously?</font>

261
00:14:33,080 --> 00:14:35,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yours truly has the cleanest hands.</font>

262
00:14:35,330 --> 00:14:38,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I, uh, just remembered
I don't like fries that much.</font>

263
00:14:38,830 --> 00:14:39,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You don't?</font>

264
00:14:39,920 --> 00:14:42,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Rikka really loves the fries here.</font>

265
00:14:43,460 --> 00:14:45,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But if you don't want them, that's fine.</font>

266
00:14:52,750 --> 00:14:54,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Give me another one.</font>

267
00:14:54,380 --> 00:14:55,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">S-Sure.</font>

268
00:15:00,130 --> 00:15:02,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">O-Oh, that reminds me.</font>

269
00:15:02,210 --> 00:15:04,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We all came here together once.</font>

270
00:15:04,330 --> 00:15:07,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It sucked when Nene stole my parfait!</font>

271
00:15:09,920 --> 00:15:14,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But Iko shared her ice cream
with me to even it out.</font>

272
00:15:16,960 --> 00:15:21,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is this about me calling
the others by their first names?</font>

273
00:15:21,670 --> 00:15:23,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Not at all.</font>

274
00:15:25,290 --> 00:15:27,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If you say so. I won't press you.</font>

275
00:15:27,630 --> 00:15:29,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are you sure about me not using yours?</font>

276
00:15:29,880 --> 00:15:32,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's fine. That would be unfair of me.</font>

277
00:15:33,750 --> 00:15:36,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Now, why don't we call it a day?</font>

278
00:15:43,250 --> 00:15:44,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The rain's not letting up.</font>

279
00:15:45,170 --> 00:15:48,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Darn it! My umbrella
got wrecked earlier, too!</font>

280
00:15:48,750 --> 00:15:52,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sorry, you got held up because of me.</font>

281
00:15:52,630 --> 00:15:54,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll share my umbrella to make up for it.</font>

282
00:16:04,500 --> 00:16:07,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Your grades have improved recently.</font>

283
00:16:07,000 --> 00:16:09,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Good to see you've
been hitting the books.</font>

284
00:16:09,420 --> 00:16:12,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's because I have a good tutor,
Yamabuki-sensei.</font>

285
00:16:12,040 --> 00:16:13,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But of course.</font>

286
00:16:14,460 --> 00:16:18,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If your grades keep improving,
you won't need me anymore.</font>

287
00:16:18,420 --> 00:16:20,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're giving me too much credit, Sensei.</font>

288
00:16:25,920 --> 00:16:27,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You know, Yamabuki-kun...</font>

289
00:16:27,920 --> 00:16:32,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I said no to being called Shinobu
because it'd be too embarrassing earlier,</font>

290
00:16:32,080 --> 00:16:34,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but it's really because I'd feel guilty.</font>

291
00:16:34,920 --> 00:16:37,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm the only one out of the four of us</font>

292
00:16:37,330 --> 00:16:39,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">who has a different
kind of dream, after all.</font>

293
00:16:40,540 --> 00:16:42,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Iko-chan's doing great, huh?</font>

294
00:16:42,250 --> 00:16:44,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You can tell?</font>

295
00:16:44,500 --> 00:16:48,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">At first, she couldn't emote on stream.
That was a big problem.</font>

296
00:16:49,330 --> 00:16:50,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Iko.</font>

297
00:16:51,080 --> 00:16:55,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You can tell what your viewers
want to hear right now, right?</font>

298
00:16:56,330 --> 00:16:59,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Now, go end the stream on a good note.</font>

299
00:17:17,920 --> 00:17:20,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Forget-It-All Beam!</font>

300
00:17:21,080 --> 00:17:23,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It was unfortunate how
that collab event ended up,</font>

301
00:17:23,880 --> 00:17:27,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but she's trying a bunch of different
things, which will help her grow.</font>

302
00:17:28,960 --> 00:17:30,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Nene-chan, too.</font>

303
00:17:30,420 --> 00:17:33,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">She's always business as usual, though.</font>

304
00:17:33,330 --> 00:17:35,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Y-You think?</font>

305
00:17:35,170 --> 00:17:39,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I mean, she went and auditioned
before I even said anything.</font>

306
00:17:40,040 --> 00:17:42,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">"I'm sorry for summoning you here."</font>

307
00:17:42,790 --> 00:17:45,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">She's practicing in secret?</font>

308
00:17:45,330 --> 00:17:49,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A soft, pleasant voice, much like
a cat that wants some love.</font>

309
00:17:49,540 --> 00:17:52,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">"Before you leave me,</font>

310
00:17:52,250 --> 00:17:54,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It really does feel familiar.</font>

311
00:17:54,000 --> 00:17:56,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">there is something I must tell you."</font>

312
00:17:56,330 --> 00:17:57,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">However...</font>

313
00:17:57,540 --> 00:17:58,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">However, I say!</font>

314
00:17:59,380 --> 00:18:01,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">- Your acting downright sucks!
- E-Eek!</font>

315
00:18:01,830 --> 00:18:05,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">...won't you tell me
that you love me once more?</font>

316
00:18:05,080 --> 00:18:08,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I think and I think and I think...</i></font>

317
00:18:11,290 --> 00:18:14,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Y-Yep... I love you...</font>

318
00:18:15,170 --> 00:18:18,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Her portrayal of things she's
unfamiliar with needs a lot of work.</font>

319
00:18:19,250 --> 00:18:20,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But...</font>

320
00:18:20,420 --> 00:18:22,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">when she does put in the work...</font>

321
00:18:23,460 --> 00:18:25,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I don't want to see your
stupid mug ever again.</font>

322
00:18:25,630 --> 00:18:26,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Get out of my sight.</font>

323
00:18:27,330 --> 00:18:31,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">She's capable of acting
that chills yours truly to the bone.</font>

324
00:18:31,670 --> 00:18:33,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I kinda want to see it.</font>

325
00:18:35,170 --> 00:18:38,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Rikka-chan's made progress, too.</font>

326
00:18:38,500 --> 00:18:41,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes, thanks to you all.</font>

327
00:18:42,710 --> 00:18:46,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Rikka became capable of
singing her own songs again.</font>

328
00:18:46,830 --> 00:18:48,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yay!</font>

329
00:18:48,750 --> 00:18:52,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh? Why are you all here?
Where are the other spectators?</font>

330
00:18:53,250 --> 00:18:54,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sorry...</font>

331
00:18:54,130 --> 00:18:55,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">- Rikka!
- Rikka-chan!</font>

332
00:18:57,830 --> 00:19:01,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}You always put up a front
and never tell us anything.</font>

333
00:19:01,210 --> 00:19:03,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}You should at least vent to us sometimes.</font>

334
00:19:03,500 --> 00:19:08,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}We kinda made these sloppy last-minute,
but we'll do better when it's for reals.</font>

335
00:19:08,380 --> 00:19:12,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Imagine we're always in the front row.</font>

336
00:19:12,920 --> 00:19:16,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Just look at us when it gets tough, okay?</font>

337
00:19:20,500 --> 00:19:22,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah, okay.</font>

338
00:19:26,580 --> 00:19:28,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I can't wait for her street performance.</font>

339
00:19:37,330 --> 00:19:40,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>They all took a step closer</i>
<i>to their dreams.</i></font>

340
00:19:42,380 --> 00:19:44,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>That helped them get</i>
<i>closer to you as well.</i></font>

341
00:19:53,880 --> 00:19:59,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>The gap between us and our dreams</i>
<i>becomes the gap between us and you.</i></font>

342
00:20:00,670 --> 00:20:03,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Which means I'm dead last right now.</i></font>

343
00:20:05,920 --> 00:20:09,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I mean, after all...</i></font>

344
00:20:12,330 --> 00:20:13,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's wrong?</font>

345
00:20:17,420 --> 00:20:18,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Nothing.</font>

346
00:20:21,080 --> 00:20:23,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I'm having so much fun</i>
<i>studying with you every week</i></font>

347
00:20:24,080 --> 00:20:27,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>that I'm actually hoping</i>
<i>my grades won't get better,</i></font>

348
00:20:27,960 --> 00:20:30,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>and I can keep studying with you</i>
<i>instead of pursuing my dream.</i></font>

349
00:20:33,170 --> 00:20:35,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>What a silly thing to wish for.</i></font>

350
00:20:42,130 --> 00:20:45,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Right now, "Uzuki" is good enough for me.</i></font>

351
00:20:46,080 --> 00:20:47,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>In return,</i></font>

352
00:20:48,250 --> 00:20:51,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I want to enjoy these times</i>
<i>for a bit longer.</i></font>

353
00:20:53,880 --> 00:20:55,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>But one day...</i></font>

354
00:20:59,960 --> 00:21:02,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Actually, Yamabuki-kun...</font>

355
00:21:05,380 --> 00:21:10,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>If I can ever hold my head high</i>
<i>and say I'm chasing my dream...</i></font>

356
00:21:13,420 --> 00:21:15,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If I can ever...</font>

357
00:21:19,830 --> 00:21:22,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If I ever manage to make big
strides towards my dream...</font>

358
00:21:33,080 --> 00:21:36,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and stand alongside those three one day...</font>

359
00:21:37,920 --> 00:21:39,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">When that time comes,</font>

360
00:21:51,460 --> 00:21:52,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">will you...</font>

361
00:22:04,380 --> 00:22:06,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">call me by my first name then?</font>

362
00:22:06,960 --> 00:22:09,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}BLACK CATS AND WHITE DOGS</font>

363
00:22:12,250 --> 00:22:17,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}TRANSLATION: SRIRAM GURUNATHAN
TIMING: MARIANA MARTINEZ
EDITING: WILLIAM HAGGARD</font>

